Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.74,0:02:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh! It's so chilly! \NLet's hurry up inside the greenhouse. {g, no clue what's first two words}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.22,0:02:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
