Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.97,0:02:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Warm!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.38,0:02:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like spring has come.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.91,0:02:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it wonderful? So many different flowers!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.49,0:02:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Taru-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.46,0:02:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's good to be carefree like Taru.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.34,0:02:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I should've brought Iyona-chan along too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.28,0:02:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Mimora!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.40,0:02:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.86,0:03:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright. Time to find out what Mimora-chan wants!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.28,0:03:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.23,0:03:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Caught you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.81,0:03:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I am so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.08,0:03:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru-sama? Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.84,0:03:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Me okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.32,0:03:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.16,0:03:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you, Taru!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.18,0:03:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Always so clingy and flirty with Mimora-chan...! {clinging (e.g. of a person); following around; being all over (each other); flirting​ - unsure, maybe "receiving .. from mimiora"}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.15,0:03:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let it slide!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.58,0:03:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Rival! The thing with girls is, \Nyou need to enamor them using your own power.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.80,0:03:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Screwing over your rival in love \Nwill get you nowhere. {to trap (into a difficult situation); to put (in a fix); to throw (e.g. into turmoil); to trick (into doing); to lure (into a trap); to frame (for a crime)}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.42,0:03:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,If fact, doing so is very cowardly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.86,0:03:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm no coward!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.82,0:03:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll use my own power to wrest \NMimora-chan's heart out of his claws!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.04,0:03:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru-sama! Aren't the flowers beautiful?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.81,0:03:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.78,0:04:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.84,0:04:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Flowers are friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.43,0:04:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's sing togetheru-ru-ru!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.22,0:04:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.34,0:04:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And you love everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.60,0:04:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone also loves me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.45,0:04:27.49,Default,,0,0,10,,{\an8}Let's go around and tell everyone! {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.89,0:04:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you be that childish?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.51,0:04:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What's all this crap about being "friends with flowers"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.86,0:04:35.46,Default,,0,0,10,,{\an8}Together, together!{g}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.27,0:04:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just a sissy, Taruruuto! {effeminate; unmanly; cowardly; sissy}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.69,0:04:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't Taru-sama's magic wonderful?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.65,0:04:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm mesmerized!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.82,0:04:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I love flowers so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.60,0:04:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I see! Mimora-chan loves flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.30,0:04:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright. My present will be this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.78,0:05:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? Did someone hurt you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.51,0:05:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a bug!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.43,0:05:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What now, just some bug? Don't scare me like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.00,0:05:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Come.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.37,0:05:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Bugs are friends too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.56,0:05:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Not for me. I... I think, bugs are...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.92,0:05:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.01,0:05:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.90,0:05:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.00,0:05:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru-sama, take it away!{g}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.86,0:05:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Mimora-chan, I'll save you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.87,0:05:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Don't you bully Mimora-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.50,0:05:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Mimora-chan has me to protect her!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.74,0:05:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.59,0:05:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Rival... Sneakily attacking Taru-sama like that...{/suddenly}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.82,0:05:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the final straw!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.61,0:05:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the final one for sure! {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.70,0:06:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did she do that!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.45,0:06:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What can I do to make Mimora-chan happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.57,0:06:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,This flower ate the bug!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.58,0:06:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing! This flower is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.96,0:06:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Mimora-chan loves flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.54,0:06:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And Mimora-chan hates bugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.86,0:06:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,A flower that eats insects!
