Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.76,0:06:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,This flower must become my present!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.02,0:06:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what kind of flower this is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.47,0:06:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,A beautiful one!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.15,0:06:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Mimora-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.46,0:07:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems like Rival hasn't had enough. {/coming again}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.46,0:07:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it he's carrying?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.99,0:07:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at this flower!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.76,0:07:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, where did you get it from?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.16,0:07:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What in the world is this flower?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.27,0:07:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Here. See this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.30,0:07:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Right? Ain't it disgusting?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.73,0:07:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But that disgusting insect...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.16,0:07:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,This thing is impressive!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.88,0:07:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,See? Ain't it amazing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.30,0:07:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,This flower eats insects that Mimora hates!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.39,0:07:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my present to Mimora-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.44,0:07:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep it. {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.00,0:07:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't feel so well!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.66,0:07:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And don't come near me! {g, desuwane?}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.56,0:08:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.92,0:08:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't expect a girl to be into this kind of flower.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.90,0:08:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.64,0:08:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Sniffle... {sniff; sniffle; snuffle}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.49,0:08:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Easy, easy. This isn't your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.96,0:08:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's return you to where you came from.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.18,0:08:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand, I don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.58,0:08:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Rival, if there's something you can't understand, \Nread a book and conduct research.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.27,0:08:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Right! If I consult a book, I'll be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.79,0:08:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Things that girls want...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.16,0:08:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Big plush toys and sleek cars... {g, no clue what's after ooki}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.72,0:08:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Good, good!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.90,0:08:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Special presents catalogue!{g}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.88,0:08:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. A trip, a cake... {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.73,0:08:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,A set of diamond colliers... {no clue what's this korosetto}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.89,0:08:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.50,0:09:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear customer?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.53,0:09:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright! This would be perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.12,0:09:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear customer!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.53,0:09:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I gotta hurry and get the presents!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.37,0:09:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey you! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.84,0:09:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a pretty interesting exhibit, Taru.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.52,0:09:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.24,0:09:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm happy that I got to see so many beautiful flowers!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.81,0:09:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Me happy too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.80,0:09:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It sure is good to be getting along.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.90,0:09:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Mimora-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.77,0:09:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's your present!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.48,0:09:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.08,0:09:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Mimora-chan, everything you see here \Nis my present to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.70,0:10:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you amazed?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.71,0:10:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you alright, Taru-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.31,0:10:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Rival, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.66,0:10:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,This... Everything for Mimora-chan, my pre...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.32,0:10:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep it.{/I don't want it}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.87,0:10:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go home, Taru-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.78,0:10:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry about that, Rival.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.33,0:10:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.03,0:10:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.05,0:10:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Give my car back!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.06,0:10:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't take it without paying!{g}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.00,0:10:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just mean!{g}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.39,0:10:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey you, thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.40,0:10:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it back!{g}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.68,0:10:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.68,0:11:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Rival!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.98,0:11:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.90,0:11:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Where'd you get the idea \Nthat stealing is okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.99,0:11:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Show some remorse! {regret; repentance; remorse; being sorry}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.29,0:11:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But... this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.65,0:11:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.03,0:11:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's apologize to everyone together, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.10,0:11:50.08,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&H0E0206&\3c&H745257&\fs30}Spirit, technique, strength​ {心技一体}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.02,0:11:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see what the general situation is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.34,0:12:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,However, even doing it for Mimora-chan \Ncan't be a justification for stealing, Rival.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.99,0:12:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.83,0:12:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.90,0:12:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,As for the present for Mimora-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.04,0:12:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,On your path to conquering the heart\Nof the woman you love, you'll make countless mistakes.{h}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.11,0:12:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But losing your heart \Nover each such mistake is a no-go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.68,0:12:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.30,0:12:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,If you correct your behaviour,\Nuse your head, and put in your every effort,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.88,0:12:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,your dreams will come true someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.92,0:12:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Fight on, Rival.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.06,0:12:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.66,0:12:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.24,0:12:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.64,0:12:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The transformation belt should help!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.68,0:12:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Transformation!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.66,0:12:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Turning Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.31,0:12:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,With this, I can learn what Mimora likes,\Nstraight from the horse's mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.59,0:13:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mimora-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.61,0:13:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Honmaru-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.00,0:13:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What in the world happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.91,0:13:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.62,0:13:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Mimora-chan, what do you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.56,0:13:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this question, all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.64,0:13:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I was wondering, just for kicks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.52,0:13:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so naughty, Honmaru-sama! {/this won't work}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.12,0:13:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately for you, \NTaru-sama is already the love of my life.{/the most loved person}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.54,0:13:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That little shit...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.51,0:13:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Little... Oh, little star, \Nhow I wonder what you are... {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.43,0:13:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a popular song these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.52,0:13:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru-sama is weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.02,0:13:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Mimora-chan. I wasn't asking who you love.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.85,0:13:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, I wanna know what things you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.42,0:13:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I like summer a great deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.86,0:13:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not what I meant! \NWhat about things? Things you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.37,0:13:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me think...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.04,0:13:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I also like sunflowers quite a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.31,0:13:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. A sunflower, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.27,0:13:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright! A sunflower it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.10,0:13:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?{g}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.09,0:14:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give Mimora-chan the best present!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.66,0:14:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,One sunflower, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.80,0:14:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.06,0:14:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you say a sunflower?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.50,0:14:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.72,0:14:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if we have any by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.40,0:14:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Manager, do we have any sunflowers?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.59,0:14:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? What? Sunflowers in the win—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.06,0:14:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! It's you! Back at it already?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.88,0:14:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.19,0:14:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,"Sunflowers in the winter," my butt!\NDon't you dare come back again!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.28,0:14:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.45,0:14:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. Sunflowers only grow in the summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.19,0:14:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright! In that case, I'll search far and wide \Nto bring you some sunflowers! {/through the world}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.86,0:14:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Sunflowers, sunflowers... Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.65,0:15:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Found them! The sunflowers!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.20,0:15:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru-sama, it's so cold outside these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.22,0:15:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh it's snowing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.66,0:15:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my! It's snowing indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.00,0:15:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Freezing! {g, tlc}{15:34: I'm hearing "ちべたい"\NThis might just be a corruption of "冷たい (つめたい)"}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.68,0:15:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So beautiful...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.08,0:15:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay! Snowing, snowing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.63,0:15:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru-sama, that's so like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.52,0:15:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.05,0:15:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,This will delight Mimora-chan to no end!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.57,0:15:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So cold...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.64,0:15:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I gotta present it soon!{/give}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.02,0:15:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.48,0:16:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! It's no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.21,0:16:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Flying through the sky makes it scatter!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.19,0:16:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I gotta hurry. Mimora-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.95,0:16:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Please wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.09,0:16:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,She went out to play?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.77,0:16:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Goddammit! It's that Taru again...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.88,0:16:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Sunflower, will you hang on?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.77,0:16:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Mimora-chan, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.98,0:16:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it, Taru-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.70,0:16:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Taru! Let's have a snowball fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.58,0:16:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.77,0:16:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.40,0:16:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You two can join forces. \NLet's do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.91,0:16:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine by me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.19,0:16:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright. Commence the battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.09,0:16:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Unfair! {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.64,0:16:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That was sly, Honmaru-sama. {/unfair}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.30,0:16:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Speed is the essence of battle! {lit: that was my fast victory in the fight}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.26,0:16:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru wide open! {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.58,0:16:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no! You missed!{g}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.92,0:17:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow-ow-ow! Oh no... It's cold.{g}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.48,0:17:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru-sama so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.46,0:17:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H181E6D&}Dammit...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.73,0:17:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch out, Mimora! {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.65,0:17:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not done yet! {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.92,0:17:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Mimora-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.39,0:17:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Mimora-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.57,0:17:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.03,0:17:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,No... My sunflower!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.22,0:17:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank god...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.62,0:17:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You're safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.28,0:18:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's hurry up and find Mimora-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.89,0:18:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so good at it, Taru-sama! Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.58,0:18:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.61,0:18:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You wanna play serious?!{g}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.16,0:18:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Come and get it!{g}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.03,0:18:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,There, there, there, there, there!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.83,0:18:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru, come! {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.05,0:18:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Mimora-chan! {g, by the fact they stop and look at rival}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.38,0:18:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Rival.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.92,0:18:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Mimora-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.50,0:18:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up with you, Rival?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.61,0:18:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Here. A present for Mimora-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.44,0:18:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.61,0:18:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.18,0:18:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,A sunflower.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.63,0:18:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.98,0:18:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Mimora-chan's favorite, the sunflower!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.14,0:18:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That's one tattered sunflower.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.33,0:18:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Why'd you do such a cruel thing to it, Rival? {no clue what she means by "what a pitiful thing doing"}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.25,0:18:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Sunflowers cannot live in the cold! {g, no clue what's this gatteru}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.57,0:18:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Return it to where you found it at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.53,0:18:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.88,0:19:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't be serious...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.46,0:19:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's a present...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.00,0:19:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel kinda sorry for Rival.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.15,0:19:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,He went to all the trouble of bringing it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.48,0:19:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Mimora, accept the sunflower.{h}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.32,0:19:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my! Taru-sama is always so considerate!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.62,0:19:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.86,0:19:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,If Taru-sama says so, I accept it.{/take}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.96,0:19:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Good for you, Rival.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.71,0:19:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't do anything this wicked ever again!{no clue}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.19,0:19:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Rival, let's have a snowball fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.66,0:19:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.16,0:19:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Rival!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.66,0:19:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never be friends with your kind!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.93,0:19:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you kidding me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.19,0:19:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You fools! {could be only mimora/taru}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.23,0:20:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, so he actually went the extra mile.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.26,0:20:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Rival-kun worked really hard to get me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.34,0:20:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,He was sure I'd delight Mimora-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.26,0:20:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,He put in his every effort to bring here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.04,0:20:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.67,0:20:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Rival can be a nice guy too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.86,0:20:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Rival friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.86,0:20:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I was an idiot... {lit: if only I had ...}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.44,0:20:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Rival? What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.68,0:20:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Mimora-chan came, saying she wants to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.16,0:20:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I refuse!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.12,0:20:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure, Rival?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.12,0:21:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Rival, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.38,0:21:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Sunflower-san told me everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.57,0:21:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, come out to meet me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.21,0:21:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like it's to no avail, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.46,0:21:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright. With his wisdom, \NHonmaru-sama will come in clutch. {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.10,0:21:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you really?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.00,0:21:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes I can!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.25,0:21:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Mimora-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.38,0:21:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, wake up, Rival.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.00,0:21:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's jogging time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.40,0:21:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's snowing outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.49,0:21:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Running in the snow is the best \Nfor training your stamina.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.76,0:21:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.48,0:21:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't we skip just today?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.38,0:21:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Rival! Come see this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.97,0:21:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.41,0:21:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, hurry! \NYou need to see this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.08,0:21:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.34,0:21:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You did it, Rival.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.80,0:22:03.77,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&HA7788B&\3c&HBECBBE&\fs30}I'm sorry, Rival🖤 \NThanks for the sunflower!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.35,0:22:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,A message from Mimora-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.66,0:22:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,"I'm sorry, Rival...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.36,0:22:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the sunflower...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.82,0:22:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Mimora-chan."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.88,0:22:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you glad, Rival?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.00,0:22:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.13,0:22:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Behold, myself - the Great Magician Ria Kinakamo.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.47,0:22:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make your one wish come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.88,0:22:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a story from a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.35,0:22:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Though it started from a coincidence for Ria and Gosuke, {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.46,0:22:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,fueled by genuine kindness, \Nthe love became real.{g}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.88,0:22:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you will...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.59,0:22:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll find someone wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.94,0:23:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Magical Taruruuto-kun: \NRia's Love Story. {りあの愛の物語}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.52,0:23:02.03,Sign,,0,0,0,,Episode 74 \NRia's Love Story {りあの愛の物語}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.07,0:23:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll send you a warm heart.{g}
